product.title_excluding_brand: 7 in 1 Hair Styler & Hair Dryer Brush, 110,000 RPM High-Speed Blow Dryer with Negative Ions for Frizz-Free Styling Fast Drying Curling Volumizing Straightening, Hot Air Styler with Travel Case
product.description:
7-IN-1Air Styling & Drying System,Your Personal Stylist, Unleashing Your Charm High-Speed Hair Dryer &Styling Concentrator



This high-speed hair dryer features a magnetic nozzle forprecise airflow control. With 110,000 RPM and 28 m/s airflow, itcuts drying time by 50% and reduces heat damage compared toother dryers.



Oval-Shaped Curling Brush
Direct airflow to the roots for quick drying. Effortlessly createvoluminous styles, leaving hair dry, smooth, and sleek.



Diffuser Attachment of Hair Dryers
Designed to enhance the natural curls of the hair, the diffuserreduces frizz effectively with gentle and even airflow, maintainingthe shape and elasticity of curls.



Automatic curling & styling
The automatic curling iron is equipped with Coanda technologySimply place a strand of hair near the curling iron, and it willautomatically curl, creating voluminous curls quickly.



Straightener Brushcomb and Flat lron in one
The Easywave hot air brush utilizes negative ion technology tostraighten and smooth hair, reduce frizz and static, leaving hairsmoother and more manageable.



Specifications:
Voltage: 120V, 50/60Hz
Power: 1100-1200W
Noise: ≤ 82 dB
Wind speed: ≥ 15m/s
Motor: BLDC high-speed brushless motor, speed 11W.
Four mode: cold air mode - low heat mode - high heat mode - cold hot cycle mode
Casing material: PC
Power cord: 2.5M 360° rotation
Protection: constant temperature protection

Travel Case*1 * ‌7-IN-1 HAIR STYLER SET - Easywave hot air styler combines the functions of a hairdryer and a multi-purpose styling tool. It includes 7 attachments for scalp massage, fast drying, straightening, curling, volumizing, and creating fluffy styles. Our styling tool is equipped with a high-speed brushless motor, reducing vibration and noise. It delivers a powerful airflow of 28 m/s and 110,000 RPM, drying hair three times faster than traditional hair dryers.
 * 35MM AUTO-WRAP CURLERS - Equipped with left and right auto-rotating curling barrels, it utilizes the Coanda effect to attract and wrap hair more effectively for fast styling. The curling iron features an aluminum alloy body with ceramic coating technology, ensuring durability, maintaining a constant safe temperature, and provides even heat distribution to prevent hair damage from overheating. 2-hour salon curls, 4-hour hold with hairspray.
 * SMART TEMPERATURE CONTROL - The hair dryer brush features four temperature settings (cold, warm, hot, and alternating) and three speed settings, easily adjustable with the up and down buttons. Equipped with smart temperature control utilizes sensors and a microprocessor, it adjusts airflow temperature 1000 times per second to ensure it stays below 176°F, protecting hair from heat damage.
 * NEGATIVE IONS AND SMOOTHING BRUSH - The Easywave hot air brush releases negative ions during use to prevent static electricity, effectively reducing frizz and leaving hair smoother and more resilient. The oval volumizer brush features a design with nylon pins and tufted bristles, effortlessly detangling hair, minimizing breakage, and creating a smooth, healthy style.
 * COMFORT AND SAFETY - Featuring ergonomically designed buttons, the blow dryer weighs only 1 pound, allowing for easy one-handed operation and mode switching. The 360° rotating power cord ensures convenient use. Equipped with an NTC feedback system, a bimetallic thermal switch, and a non-resettable fuse, air styler also includes an ALCI safety plug with overheating protection and electric shock prevention.
